156 Section 3. The following are repealed:
157 (1) Act 84-618 of the 1984 Regular Session (Acts 1984,
158 p. 1256), providing for an expense allowance for the mayor of
159 a Class 1 municipality.
160 (2) Section 11-42-86.1, Code of Alabama 1975, providing
161 for an increase in the salary of the mayor in a Class 1
162 municipality.
163 (3) Section 45-37A-52.93, Code of Alabama 1975,
164 providing for the salary of the Mayor of Birmingham.
165 Section 4. This act shall become effective immediately.
